4→    FOR EACH ROW\n    55→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n    56→\n    57→CREATE TRIGGER trigger_authors_meta_updated_at\n    58→    BEFORE UPDATE ON authors\n    59→    FOR EACH ROW\n    60→    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at\n    61→\n    62→COMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n    63→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"uuid":"74462d29-5884-404b-8b5d-4be01c5f896b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:06:25.282Z","toolUseResult":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku/apps/api/migrations/000001_add_courses.up.sql","content":"CREATE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n  NEW._updated_at = NOW();\n  RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\n\nCREATE EXTENSION ltree;\n\nCREATE TABLE \"categories\" (\n    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    name TEXT NOT NULL,\n    path ltree NOT NULL,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\nCREATE TABLE \"authors\" (\n    author_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    display_id TEXT UNIQUE,\n    name TEXT,\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n)\n\nCREATE TABLE \"courses\" (\n    course_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    title TEXT NOT NULL,\n    description TEXT NOT NULL,\n    slug TEXT NOT NULL,\n    tags JSONB NOT NULL,\n    publish_status TEXT NOT NULL,\n    category_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES categories(category_id),\n    published_at TIMESTAMPTZ,\n    last_updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,\n    author_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES authors(author_id),\n\n    _created_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n    _updated_at TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_courses_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON courses\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_categories_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON categories\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at();\n\nCREATE TRIGGER trigger_authors_meta_updated_at\n    BEFORE UPDATE ON authors\n    FOR EACH ROW\n    EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at\n\nCOMMENT ON COLUMN courses.publish_status IS 'draft / published / archived';\n","numLines":63,"startLine":1,"totalLines":63}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"feb979ab-fbf3-4c4d-b98b-e06978470220","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"88782de8-0a85-4289-a5bc-4e211e3ee724","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"snappy-bouncing-castle"}
{"parentUuid":"74462d29-5884-404b-8b5d-4be01c5f896b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01SthtPG4FvT7c8gfKyDy6xG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"以下の問題を見つけました。\n\n**バグ（修正必須）**\n\n1. **`TIMESTAMPZ` タイポ（26-27行目）** — `authors` テーブルの `_created_at` / `_updated_at` が `TIMESTAMPZ` になっている（正しくは `TIMESTAMPTZ`）\n2. **`authors` テーブルの末尾セミコロン欠落（28行目）** — `CREATE TABLE \"authors\" (...)` の閉じ括弧の後にセミコロンがない\n3. **`trigger_authors_meta_updated_at` のセミコロン欠落（60行目）** — `EXECUTE FUNCTION update_meta_updated_at` の末尾にセミコロンがない\n4. **`update_meta_updated_at()` の呼び出しに括弧がない（60行目）** — `update_meta_updated_at` → `update_meta_updated_at()`\n\n**ルール違反**\n\n5. **`display_id` と `name` に `NOT NULL` がない（23-24行目）** — ルールに「初期値は不要」とあるが、`NOT NULL` がなく NULL が許容されている。これはアプリ側が常に値を生成する前提に反する可能性があります（設計意図を確認してください）\n\n**軽微な指摘**\n\n6. **`CREATE EXTENSION ltree` にセミコロンはある** — OK ですが、慣例として `IF NOT EXISTS` を付けると安全（任意）\n\n修正しますか？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":879,"cache_read_input_tokens":7356,"output_tokens":424,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":879,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZJimF9umhDw7MK1DsV4h","type":"assistant","uuid":"d9a7bb17-6577-41c2-b60d-ec861b78a5f2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T20:06:34.224Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"88782de8-0a85-4289-a5bc-4e211e3ee724","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main","slug":"snappy-bouncing-castle"}
